extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Store Inventory], a very basic Express website.

  h1 Dynamic content

  p The inventory has the following record counts:

  ul
    li #[strong Items:] !{item_count}
      if item_in_stock_count
          li #[strong Total Items in Stock:] !{item_in_stock_count[0].total}
      else 
        li #[strong No Items in stock]
    li #[strong Categories:] !{category_count}
